functions.funcBody:
const environment = window.BKPAAS_ENVIRONMENT
const self = environment === 'preview' ? window.parent : window
const cUrl = encodeURIComponent(self.location.href)
const loginUrl = `{LOGIN_URL}/?app_code=&c_url=${cUrl}`
self.location.href = loginUrl
functions.funcSummary: 退出登陆，并跳转到登陆页面
